	(text "yes this is bad to have the analog traces running next \nto these 10mhz ~50ns or less rise time spi traces\nhowever the adc does have pretty heavy (~2.5 or so khz) \nlow pass filtering on its inputs. and this analog reading \nisnt that critical.\n\nnot connecting an exc+ and exc- so that i dont couple noise into \nthe more important load cell readings"
